replies.body:
I'm gonna go out on a limb and guess its on your first death every game. It happens to me every game, my first death causes my game to freeze for a second. It seemed like it was right before my death but I've been assured by a Riot member that it only freezes when the game decides I'm dead.
I can't recall when this bug first appeared in my game but it's been around for me for a while now. Hope this helped! 
{{summoner:4}}
